2.title: Morning After
2.plot: After Marcy leaves Jack on Rodeo Drive he bumps into Amy, a seemingly innocent girl.

imdb.plot outline: Jack, is a lonely and down on his luck Lost Angeleno, who faces rejection all day at work and lacks the confidence to be successful with the opposite sex. At night he finds comfort in the bottle which helps him escape his self-loathing and become a legend with the ladies and Hollywood night life. His problem is he wakes up and can't remember where he was or how he meets all the hot girls he hooks up with. Every day he has to confront Another Blackout and piece together the fragmented memories of his night.
imdb.title: Another Blackout
plot: Jack tries to keep it together, but every day he wakes up to...ANOTHER BLACKOUT!!!

Jack, is a lonely and down on his luck Lost Angeleno, who faces rejection all day at work and lacks the confidence to be successful with the opposite sex. At night he finds comfort in the bottle which helps him escape his self-loathing and become a legend with the ladies and Hollywood night life. His problem is he wakes up and can't remember where he was or how he meets all the hot girls he hooks up with. Every day he has to confront _Another Blackout_ (qv) and piece together the fragmented memories of his night.::Cynthia Posner and Kash Hovey
